    {
      "title": "Big trucks, big fun: Family Fun Day returns to celebrate public works professionals",
      "summary": "On Saturday, August 8, the City of Mississauga is celebrating its public works professionals and the important work they do with a free Family Fun Day event – and you’re invited! The City hosts Family Fun Day each year in May during National Public Works Week. This year, the May event was cancelled due to rain and has been rescheduled to August 8 outside City Hall. The City’s public works professionals help keep Mississauga residents and visitors safe and moving.",
